Package org.yamcs.http.websocket

Interface WebSocketDecoder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonDecoder, ProtobufDecoder
    public interface WebSocketDecoder
    Used to indicate to the WebSocketServerHandler what type of message can be decoded in a specific media representation.

    Current implementations need to at least support decoding the envelope, and are assumed to support all operations. In the future, we could break the API in two (1. envelope, 2. payload) if we ever get to a point of needing that.
